Package: lithememgr-qt
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, listaller
Replaces: lithememgr-gtk
Description: liTheme Manager (Qt4)
  Tool that lets you easily install/uninstall system themes, wallpapers, 
  iconsets and screensavers.  liThemeMgr is part of the Listaller project
  and uses it's technology.
  liThemeMgr is still under development. This is an daily-build and should not be used!

Package: listaller-gtk-dbg
Architecture: any
Depends: listaller-gtk (= ${binary:Version})
Description: Debug symbols for Listaller GTK tools
  This package contains the debuginfos for the Listaller base tools (GTK+ version)

Package: listaller-tools-dbg
Architecture: any
Depends: listaller-tools (= ${binary:Version})
Description: Debug symbols for Listaller command-line tools
  This package contains the debug symbols for the Listaller command-line tools
  ('lipa' and 'unibuild')

Package: listaller-creation-gtk-dbg
Architecture: any
Depends: listaller-creation-gtk (= ${binary:Version})
Description: Debug symbols for Listaller Creator (GTK+)
  This package contains the debuginfos for the IPS script
  wizard GUI (liCreator) in GTK version.

Package: lithememgr-gtk-dbg
Architecture: any
Depends: lithememgr-gtk (= ${binary:Version})
Description: Debug symbols for liTheme Manager
  This package contains the debuginfos for the Listaller theme installer
  and manager. (Symbols for GTK+ version)
